comment: Randolph (MEM) makes marginal contact with Leonard (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Conley (MEM) sets the screen on Mills (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Leonard (SAS) makes contact to Carter's (MEM) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lee (SAS) makes marginal contact with Ennis III (MEM) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Green (MEM) clamps the arm of Lee (SAS) and affects his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Green (MEM) maintains legal guarding position as Leonard (SAS) drives to the basket.
Parker (SAS) makes incidental contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his ability to defend the play.
Green (MEM) and Mills (SAS) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Carter (MEM) commits a take foul on Parker (SAS).
Ennis III (MEM) commits a take foul on Leonard (SAS).
Aldridge (SAS) makes contact to Conley's (MEM) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Conley (MEM) was attempting a 3pt field goal when fouled stands.
[Observable in enhanced video] Parker (SAS) enters the area inside the three-point line prior to the free throw being released.
Conley (MEM) commits a take foul on Green (SAS).
[Observable in enhanced video] Daniels (MEM) enters the area inside the three-point line prior to the free throw being released.
Mills (SAS) makes marginal contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his SQBR.
Joseph (TOR) and Dellavedova (MIL) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Patterson (TOR) makes contact to the body of Antetokounmpo (MIL) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (TOR) and Monroe (MIL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
[Observable in enhanced video] DeRozan (TOR) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Patterson (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his SQBR.
DeRozan (TOR) jumps from point A to point B, but does not initiate the marginal contact to the body with Middleton (MIL).
Dellavedova (MIL) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his FOM.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of TOR possession stands.
Terry (MIL) makes contact to DeRozan's (TOR) arm that affects his SQBR on the dunk attempt.
Maker (MIL) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (TOR) on the dunk attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes body to body contact with DeRozan (TOR) that affects his SQBR.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Joseph (TOR).
[Incidental or immaterial] Monroe (MIL) grabs and holds DeRozan (TOR) off ball.
Ibaka (TOR) grabs and pulls Middleton's (MIL) jersey and the contact affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Middleton (MIL) was attempting a 3pt field goal when fouled is confirmed.
Terry (MIL) dislodges DeRozan's (TOR) hand from the ball and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of TOR possession is overturned and MIL is awarded possession.
Lowry (TOR) legally contests Terry's (MIL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Terry (MIL) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
[Observable in enhanced video] Snell (MIL) enters the paint area prior to the free throw being released.
Joseph (TOR) makes marginal contact with Dellavedova (MIL) that does not affect his FOM.
Snell (MIL) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
